{"tid":785982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爭鮮舊post被考古　6年前推介虹鱒餐盒","createTime":"2018-08-19T15:45:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T03:54:23.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"11b94505399fc202ca3d26a7505b245197677bb6","tid":785982,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T15:45:56.000Z","msg":"作者：熱血編輯部 (陳五) 08-19-2018 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/201808/20180819fish.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F201808%2F20180819fish.jpg&h=3134aa3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國有水產業團體近日發布自訂的《生食三文魚》團體標準，將淡水養殖虹鱒，歸類為「三文魚」，引起連串爭議。究竟在香港吃到的是虹鱒還是三文魚？來自淡水的虹鱒是否適合生食，看來要專家才能解答。 因應近日虹鱒的爭議，有網民今日（8月19日）考古，發現在香港有不少分店的爭鮮，早於6年前就推介虹鱒產品。一個2012年8月27日的爭鮮Facebook Page舊帖，就推介了一個價值24元的「鱒三文魚餐盒」，並介紹了虹鱒的來歷。 內容指虹鱒（Rainbow trout）又稱鱒三文魚，體型較一般三文魚小，對水質條件要求高，在溶氧量高的水域繁殖。體側有一漂亮的紅色帶，如同彩虹，得名「虹鱒」。 在圖示中，爭鮮以紅字標示「水質條件要求高」，但亦有提及是「棲息在低水溫且水質清澈的淡水」。 在今年8月16日，爭鮮亦在專頁發帖，指「爭鮮採用源於挪威的大西洋三文魚。經衛生檢疫出口，每日新鮮空運到港，為大家提供優質美味」。<br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/08-19-2018/47608\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F08-19-2018%2F47608&d=75dq7Log460%2Bcjd9q5mN%2F0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=09069317\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/08-19-2018/47608</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2018"},{"pid":"29195b88cf29bdd2e192d766352a732f0f72bcaa","tid":785982,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T15:49:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0poz7l3x\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0poz7l3x&h=ce771187&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a4653a3a984110d4f5d13b4af36ca5f490debf5","tid":785982,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T17:51:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1670aeb6e63887753b9c4d2c5009833f4fc32fed","tid":785982,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T01:07:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2226cf1a6ef36fc60c42865538669c26c16c358","tid":785982,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T02:45:35.000Z","msg":"賣到咁撚平（$3外賣/$8堂食）你就知伏伏地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前幫襯過兩三次都無再食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n近兩三年就直頭三文魚都戒埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"009e19ccdc3e3c21e873540db3565b8d09de50f2","tid":785982,"uid":116289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T02:46:11.000Z","msg":"爭蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a09713d3079fa561f66d0e531f6323ece369b8d","tid":785982,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T02:57:53.000Z","msg":"垃圾<br />\n好心啲港媽咪撚帶啲細路去食"},{"pid":"bb1d3276bbf909c9b2d0991f51cc447c12c7b39f","tid":785982,"uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a09713d3079fa561f66d0e531f6323ece369b8d","tid":785982,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T02:57:53.000Z","msg":"垃圾<br />\n好心啲港媽咪撚帶啲細路去食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T03:31:08.000Z","msg":"我食過一次爭鮮後, 都無再自己去食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係睇三文魚, 我未見過佢有一次係叫正常既,( 我指係新鮮), 多數唔知放左幾耐先拎出黎賣咁既款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56f73ed34263ea066ba42056effca8f3b213e569","tid":785982,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T03:54:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}